Actress Toyin Aimakhu has confirmed the relationship between Nkechi Blessing and Mike Adeyemi which many had believed to be untrue.  Nkechi Blessing posted on the social media a video of her kissing Mike Adeyemi at a beach and the caption announced him as her man.  That was at first indication believed by many to be another stunt from the brazen actress known to be restlessly controversial actress especially, especially because she had pranked on her followers with a fake marriage proposal which she later claimed to have done to promote her brand. Somewhere between the melodrama, Toyin Aimakhu, who welcomed a baby days ago has tacitly confirmed the relationship via Instagram.  She shared the lovers’ photograph and wrote: ”Hbd @official_mikeadeyemi007 thanks for making my girl @nkechiblessingsunday smile always”.